oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Summer 1966 Calendar of Events
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: entertainment; events; libraries; radio; reading; television; 1960s;
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: The calendar of events for the summer of 1966. The flyer was designed to be mailed. Events listed include story times, book discussions, film viewings, and radio and television programs.
oai_dc:dc.dc:format: red ink on yellow paper, two-sided (only one side shown), 8.5 x 11 in.
